data.description: This four bedroom, brick home is located in one of Jesup's favorite neighborhoods.  Recently updated interior with new flooring and lots of shiplap accent walls. Home is 2231 htd square feet,  4 Bedrooms, 2 full baths, living area opens to large kitchen with appliances and dining room combo, bonus family room.  Shingle roof less then 5 years old, a 16 x 20 shop, large 20x20 screened porch on rear with a two bay carport. Bonus building/ MIL tiny home optional. Gutters, storm windows and sprinkler stystem.  Corner lot . Over 5+ acres.
